<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٦٢٤ -<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ عَطَاءٍ عَنْ غَزْوَةِ الْبَحْرِ فَكَرَهَهُ وَقَالَ: <span class="c2">«أَخْشَى»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>